ch.uzh.ifi.seal.changedistiller.model.classifiers

枚举 ChangeType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ChangeType>
      • ch.uzh.ifi.seal.changedistiller.model.classifiers.ChangeType
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    Serializable, Comparable<ChangeType>

    public enum ChangeType
extends Enum<ChangeType>
    All change types that are extracted by ChangeDistiller and stored as SourceCodeChange.

    Each type contains a SignificanceLevel, is marked whether it is a body change (e.g. found inside a method body) or not and whether its significance level is unstable and may be lifted (e.g. for a method renaming, the significance gets lifted if the method is public or protected).

    作者:
    zubi
    另请参阅:
    SignificanceLevel, SourceCodeChange

        public static ChangeType[] values()
        按照声明该枚举类型的常量的顺序, 返回 包含这些常量的数组。该方法可用于迭代 常量, 如下所示: 
        for (ChangeType c : ChangeType.values())
    System.out.println(c);
        返回:
        按照声明该枚举类型的常量的顺序返回的包含这些常量的数组

      • valueOf

        public static ChangeType valueOf(String name)
        返回带有指定名称的该类型的枚举常量。 字符串必须与用于声明该类型的枚举常量的 标识符完全匹配。(不允许有多余 的空格字符。)
        参数:
        name - 要返回的枚举常量的名称。
        返回:
        返回带有指定名称的枚举常量
        抛出:
        IllegalArgumentException - 如果该枚举类型没有带有指定名称的常量
        NullPointerException - 如果参数为空值

      • isBodyChange

        public boolean isBodyChange()
        Returns whether this change is a body change or not.
        返回:
        true if this change is a body change, false if it is a declaration change.

      • isDeclarationChange

        public boolean isDeclarationChange()
        Returns whether this change is a declaration change or not.
        返回:
        true if this change is a declaration change, false if it is a body change.

      • hasUnstableSignificanceLevel

        public boolean hasUnstableSignificanceLevel()
        Returns whether the SignificanceLevel of this change may be lifted or not.
        返回:
        true if the significance level is likely to be lifted, false otherwise.
